<br>
You ask how this cleric could &quot;use you&quot; to get loot when his loot would be earned.  Here's how.<br>
<br>
I will assume that when OoD accepts someone as a full member and awards them loot, it is with the assumption that this person will continue to be an OoD member and use that loot to further the guild.  I will also assume that if you knew that this person would guildremove and apply to a higher guild once he'd gotten the loot he wanted, that you would not accept him as a member.<br>
<br>
This is how merit guild generally work.  Yes, your merit and your loot is earned, but it is with the assumption that the loot will stay with the guild.<br>
<br>
Now, someone here is warning you that one of your trials is pretending to be dedicated to OoD in order to earn his loot and then take off for another guild.<br>
<br>
If this is accpetable to you, then I suppose I will apologize for calling you stupid, even though I will secretly think that you're even dumber than I first thought.<br>
<br>
If this is not acceptable to you, then perhaps you owe an apology to the person who is trying to warn you in good faith. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/bxevserverboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=daedrea>Daedrea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered Member</span><br>  Posts: 87<br> <font color=#330000>(6/8/03 11:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=730.topic&index=39>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Loot Whores</span><hr size=1> Nerios is just a trial member.  Trial isn't anything.  If you have a pulse and an IQ over 50 I bet you could get into OoD trial.  Its 30 days long, feel free to send me a tell if you want to discuss a trial member, he will be evaluated after it is over just like every application. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=340675">Lich Daedrea Darksoul</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->65 Arch Lich<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.orderofdraconis.com">Order of Draconis</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/bxevserverboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=bippwinno>Bippwinno</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www-und.ida.liu.se/~johro897/flags/sweden.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered Member</span><br>  Posts: 192<br> <font color=#330000>(6/8/03 11:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=730.topic&index=40>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Lo